 and the kingdom: the doctrine of God|others=Translated by Margaret Kohl|edition=reprint|location=Minneapolis, MN|publisher=Fortress Press|isbn=978-0-8006-2825-3|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=D1ENDrMTaDsC&pg=PA179|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Nichols|first=Aidan|year=1995|title=Light from the East: authors and themes in Orthodox theology|series=|volume=|location=London|publisher=Sheed & Ward|isbn=978-0-7220-5081-1|url=|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Nichols|first=Aidan|year=2005|chapter=The place of the Holy Spirit in the Trinity|title=Wisdom from above: a primer in the theology of Father Sergei Bulgakov|location=Leominster|publisher=Gracewing|isbn=978-0-85244642-3|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UWTCRF7nQRMC&pg=PA157|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Nichols|first=Aidan|year=2010|title=Rome and the Eastern Churches: a study in schism|edition=2nd|location=San Francisco, CA|publisher=Ignatius Press|isbn=9781586172824|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Hje62q52XNsC&pg=PA255|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite web|author=North American Orthodox-Catholic Theological Consultation|date=2003-10-25|title=The Filioque: a Church dividing issue?|website=usccb.org|location=Washington, DC|publisher=United States Conference of Catholic Bishops|url=http://www.usccb.org/beliefs-and-teachings/ecumenical-and-interreligious/ecumenical/orthodox/filioque-church-dividing-issue-english.cfm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220120953/http://www.usccb.org/beliefs-and-teachings/ecumenical-and-interreligious/ecumenical/orthodox/filioque-church-dividing-issue-english.cfm|archivedate=2013-02-20|url-status=live|ref={{harvid|NAOCTC|2003}}}} Also archived as{{cite web|url=http://www.scoba.us/resources/orthodox-catholic/2003filioque.html |title=The Filioque: a Church-dividing issue? |accessdate=2010-06-25 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100806122533/http://www.scoba.us/resources/orthodox-catholic/2003filioque.html |archivedate=6 August 2010 |df=dmy 